comments: Nance Jr. (NOP) gathers the pass on his left foot and establishes his right foot as his pivot, which he maintains prior to releasing the pass.
Avdija (WAS) is moving alongside Williamson's (NOP) path and the body contact that occurs as they come together at the end of the drive is marginal.
Ingram (NOP) and Kispert (WAS) make incidental foot contact with each other and Kispert loses his balance as a result.
Murphy III (NOP) initiates contact with Avdija's (WAS) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) swipes down and initiates contact with McCollum's (NOP) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Poole (WAS) establishes himself in Murphy III's (NOP) path and absorbs the incoming contact before engaging and disengaging during the pick.
Ingram (NOP) reaches in and marginal body contact occurs with Avdija (WAS), who moves through it to reach the basket.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending on Williamson (NOP) is confirmed.  Williamson blocks the shot attempt after the ball reaches its apex and starts its downward trajectory.
Coulibaly (WAS) grazes Ingram's (NOP) arm at the end of the drive, which does not affect Ingram's ability to gather.
Coulibaly (WAS) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Poole (WAS) brings his hand underneath the ball and carries it to the other side of his body during his dribble.
Jones (WAS) commits a take foul on Jones (NOP).
Poole (WAS) commits a take foul on Murphy III (NOP).
Murphy III (NOP) cleanly dislodges the ball from Kispert (WAS) during his driving shot attempt.
Poole (WAS) commits a take foul on Murphy III (NOP).
Poole (WAS) does not move his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
